        Selling an Inherited Property in Queensland: A Practical Guide
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The steps between receiving an inheritance and having the legal authority to sell are often longer and more complex than people expect. This guide covers what you actually need to know.
      </p>
